= La síntesis

Every armed movement in the Republic's history died of the same disease: the city and the sierra fighting separate wars, each ignorant of the other's hours. Genaro came down to the city and was lost; the Liga went up the mountain and starved; the state, which has always been one animal, ate them one limb at a time.

This month the disease breaks. What the safe kitchen receives, the sierra reads in three days; what the sierra sees on the roads, the city knows before the convoys arrive. One nervous system, running under the Republic's skin — the thing the DFS's organizational charts insist cannot exist, because if it existed the war would stop being a hunt and become a war.

The analysts in Bucareli will need a year to believe their own reports. That year belongs to you.

- @una_guerra: One war now. Continuar.

@una_guerra
go-to: post_event

The courier who closed the loop sleeps for eighteen hours in the safe apartment, and no one wakes her. Some feats are honored in medals; here, in sleep.
